	(45, '2024-03-17 14:06:59', '2024-03-17 14:06:59', 23, 23, '清流乾坤海棠盘', 9, 7, 6899.00, 100, 'https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/74c80ae9-c583-45d8-9732-a877550a957e.jpg', '["blob:http://localhost:5174/6632d543-2517-45c5-b975-3ff8bb5949f5","blob:http://localhost:5174/4f7a39b4-8ddd-44a6-9576-20b5271ef267","blob:http://localhost:5174/d26814cc-1b94-406a-be89-21bd8de0f906","blob:http://localhost:5174/9e9c681c-97b9-4742-80be-993872b3d025","blob:http://localhost:5174/6583ebe4-4be3-4b9f-91a2-1691ed7b48ca","blob:http://localhost:5174/6f2569d3-7473-434d-b51e-6221a03c0a14"]', '清流乾坤海棠盘是一款精美的茶盘，它的设计灵感源自于故宫藏品元代王冕的“墨梅图”。盘内梅花含笑盈枝，展现出孤洁神韵，传递出“只流清气满乾坤”的志向。这款盘子采用了非遗传统工艺和朱氏釉彩铜技艺进行精制，铜材质具有抑菌性，经久耐用，健康卫生。它不仅可以搭配茶壶使用，还可以盛放糖果、点心等各种小物品，功能多样。这样的茶盘融合了传统工艺与现代实用性，展现出独特的文化价值和美感，是一件非常珍贵的艺术品。', '["https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/bfe6d27c-4288-4304-9945-01e3b3a23990.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/606bef5f-3868-49b0-868e-83b0abf7a98a.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/cfef65ec-62d8-4097-be78-fe611f8f3cc1.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/d6e2ab95-491f-4317-98d0-5374b1f92697.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/7e2683b6-1efb-44df-af86-f0386db167dd.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/9a436c5e-2a64-4791-b3b7-80bf6a786225.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/b7b76015-efad-4001-afea-67ab52cbcf83.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/d003c4a1-9779-4d8d-a4c9-c4e7e80637c4.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/25d767fb-5bc4-4a0e-882c-b7281407109a.jpg"]', '限定', 1),
	(46, '2024-03-17 14:42:30', '2024-03-17 14:42:30', 23, 23, '花开似梦系列线香', 11, 7, 199.00, 1000, 'https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/ea8bdf77-e6a0-431f-a09c-6fb25c8bf095.jpg', '["https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/e59dd3a1-9d77-4075-81af-f2b57566c85e.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/b8c42c15-19b2-421b-8043-760a5a02b3b3.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/3952651a-7c9f-4397-a3e1-d71491308694.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/6070b572-805d-44c1-901d-4f82631ea535.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/302b9058-5b53-4789-83f2-46d0d7b4c9dd.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/2926704f-5506-4c9e-b4f3-ff137978f435.jpg"]', '花开似梦系列线香是一款精致的香氛产品，以清新的花香和梦幻般的气息而闻名。这款线香采用天然植物精油和优质香料制成，散发出迷人的花香，让人仿佛置身于花海之中。\n\n花开似梦系列线香有多种香型可供选择，包括玫瑰、茉莉、樱花等，每一种香型都有着独特的魅力，能够满足不同人的喜好。线香的包装设计精美，外观典雅，适合作为家居装饰，也是送礼的不错选择。\n\n使用花开似梦系列线香，可以为生活增添一丝浪漫和温馨的氛围，让人放松身心，享受宁静的时光。不仅如此，线香的持久香味也能够净化空气，改善室内环境，是一款非常实用的香氛产品。', '["https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/89847b13-c0b1-4c9a-8be5-58d38687ea63.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/27dae475-6f03-4fcc-a195-f944d7685c79.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/70a1a493-f38c-42f2-ac68-5fb37da17763.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/f0553663-7347-4502-8d03-0908dc3c1b7f.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/8d7eece6-cb1d-4e4c-8a4e-fea4a85ab463.jpg"]', '', 1),
	(47, '2024-03-17 14:43:57', '2024-03-17 14:43:57', 23, 23, '千里江山收纳盒', 11, 7, 299.00, 1000, 'https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/875e95ab-174e-49f0-99d8-83936f51fab4.jpg', '["https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/71e16c02-e0a9-4099-819a-2cf3e17ebb30.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/1c6c021e-cb92-4903-8ba6-e11e0e97a72a.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/ae47a0c4-d8fa-440d-8422-fb3e8c462b85.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/f0266a2f-3c50-40ea-a6fb-0624055eeb83.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/48256a76-a962-4c73-a55e-6bcacd3c069f.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/6cfd67c4-3bb2-44df-b70d-04eb3ad65228.jpg"]', '千里江山收纳盒是一款设计精美的收纳盒，外观简约大方，采用高品质的环保材料制成，经久耐用。收纳盒的设计灵感源自中国传统山水画，以千里江山为主题，图案精美细致，寓意着广阔的胸怀和收纳空间。\n\n收纳盒内部结构合理，可以有效地分类收纳各种物品，如文具、首饰、化妆品等，让杂乱的物品有条不紊地摆放整齐。盒子的大小适中，方便携带和摆放，不占用过多的空间。\n\n千里江山收纳盒不仅能够让生活更加整洁有序，还可以作为家居装饰，增添一份文雅和艺术气息。无论是自用还是送礼，都是一款实用且具有美感的收纳盒。', '["https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/14a55185-7690-4fed-a70e-3560cf37730c.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/5ee6019e-0cb8-46d1-a668-5ef2e5118b2c.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/a7dbf287-6181-41c2-960d-bdb2719b6c4b.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/dc203cc7-ed01-42d6-b12d-879e1de5cc0f.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/ea62d11d-7ac6-446b-9d97-8caa4d4270d5.jpg"]', '', 1),
	(48, '2024-03-17 14:45:34', '2024-03-17 14:45:34', 23, 23, '山林清欢系列线香', 11, 7, 199.00, 1000, 'https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/c73daac0-13fe-43b9-9141-5da5957df79f.jpg', '["https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/3115f7bd-3074-4cc9-b5ce-8700ff82cd55.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/34e62aab-8de8-408e-a491-d7fd729a80a4.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/cf9df437-3c9e-4f15-9c10-2fc489398407.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/3e51ee1d-82f7-46db-998a-45252aef3c3e.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/dba4c698-e351-4d66-a119-fa66ec52068f.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/033b8cd7-4cc0-4346-a61a-cabe598c39ca.jpg"]', '山林清欢系列线香是一款清新、自然的香气产品，散发出深入山林的芳香气息。这款线香选用了天然的植物香料和精油，打造出清新的松木、柏木和竹叶等独特的山林香气，让人仿佛置身于大自然之中。\n\n山林清欢系列线香具有持久的香味，能够有效净化室内空气，带来放松和舒缓的感受。线香的包装设计简约典雅，展现出清新自然的风格，适合作为家居香氛装饰，也是送礼的不错选择。\n\n使用山林清欢系列线香，可以为生活增添一份清新自然的气息，让人感受到大自然的宁静和舒适。这款线香不仅能够提升居室的氛围，还能够带来身心的放松和愉悦，是一款非常实用的香氛产品。', '["https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/a6ff6e56-4928-4dfd-a9d0-f4a2ef1ed543.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/44ea03c8-b467-440d-86ae-e0a2f4ed900c.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/fad16b37-0839-4c77-b44e-5b7a1d4a9e43.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/da91b855-40c0-443c-8bed-fa947f288554.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/d12cbbd6-0d22-463a-a1a0-181302a54a38.jpg"]', '', 1),
	(49, '2024-03-17 14:47:40', '2024-03-17 14:47:40', 23, 23, '喜悦如意收纳盒', 11, 7, 399.00, 500, 'https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/337295f0-3cca-4483-a5e4-aedf85c938f8.jpg', '["https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/f2cf5f0b-3e77-4f02-afc1-fcf2274e022a.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/f4f8da3b-52fc-436b-84c5-cce3d51402cc.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/e182942f-53d2-4d8b-8918-ff12061c6a9c.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/f33a974e-4226-4446-b1ab-5bac91e26c0f.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/a08ca233-effa-441a-ad57-dbe941a8a14a.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/9c0132b6-7146-413b-b495-37f0712a8aa3.jpg"]', '喜悦如意收纳盒是一款设计精美的收纳容器，外观充满了喜庆和美好的意象。它通常采用优质的环保材料制成，具有良好的耐用性和质感。收纳盒的设计通常寓意着幸福如意，常常搭配一些吉祥图案或者祝福语，适合用来收纳珠宝、首饰、文具或其他小件物品。它不仅能够帮助整理物品，还能为居室增添一份幸福的氛围。这样的收纳盒在生活中也可以作为一份美好的礼物，用来表达对他人的祝福和关怀。喜悦如意收纳盒是一款设计精美的收纳容器，外观充满了喜庆和美好的意象。', '["https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/be6a0baa-e6ec-4045-acbf-8f0c2f42183d.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/0d220c6e-3622-41db-8c73-08e2070bfc70.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/e6d3a2f8-7cfb-477f-a25a-2de2fd35bf43.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/31a62b7d-252a-49f9-ac0f-a4c94440b244.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/f5afdaa5-1cd0-4a9e-a926-d5ba0080e6c1.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/09182c1a-2426-473a-be53-2bc7aa14a361.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/a0b9fa6b-de04-45fb-8cc0-50e75c7b8d53.jpg"]', '限定', 1),
	(50, '2024-03-17 14:49:07', '2024-03-17 14:49:07', 23, 23, '春玉满堂系列白玉首饰', 8, 7, 12999.00, 500, 'https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/efcdb559-f1f0-4390-b1f5-9ea25b61209a.jpg', '["https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/f91fdef1-d3c8-4b64-b80f-98870f993f63.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/6ce52360-f1f6-4483-84ef-a5e0427566da.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/d42c8d05-6ba9-42a8-91fe-f7d8da2c4ed8.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/0571dfb4-3ce9-4406-9b98-7c5fe9f1e42a.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/464a334d-72a9-4ffe-bfae-75af6d0a91e4.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/241bafde-c9bd-4ae9-ba13-b4fd76fa1e2e.jpg"]', '春玉满堂系列白玉首饰是一系列精美的珠宝首饰，以白玉为主要材料，设计时尚典雅。白玉在中国传统文化中象征着纯洁和吉祥，因此这款首饰系列常常寓意着吉祥如意、幸福美满。首饰设计精美，包括项链、手镯、耳环等，每件都展现了高品质的工艺和精湛的设计。白玉的自然纹理和光泽使得每件首饰看起来独一无二，散发着迷人的光芒。这些首饰不仅适合日常佩戴，也是搭配正装的完美选择，展现出优雅与高贵。春玉满堂系列白玉首饰不仅能够提升整体气质，还能成为送礼的不错选择，传达祝福和美好的愿望。', '["https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/660a7c80-9e59-44bd-8506-7a31cd32a12c.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/2eaf78a1-9c18-4f4e-98bc-32563497a68b.jpg"]', '玉石', 1),
	(51, '2024-03-17 14:50:22', '2024-03-17 14:50:22', 23, 23, '福禄迭至水晶手串', 8, 7, 8999.00, 300, 'https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/938f9eda-d219-467c-9981-5516a3cd1ca4.jpg', '["https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/ace49279-585f-4906-abbc-2e97020250e1.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/3b0e18ca-0438-401b-b9e1-b7becb5fd31f.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/862d251e-dc9f-42ff-8aa2-df72a905265b.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/eff9105d-70e3-4eea-8ed3-d6e58f8e3d10.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/6463282d-d8ce-44b0-8e93-ed389730ad14.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/8e19a847-3ba7-4a8d-b037-9c3177f507bd.jpg"]', '福禄迭至水晶手串是一种具有独特寓意的手饰，以水晶材质制成，寓意着福禄寿喜齐至。水晶被认为具有净化和平衡能量的功效，能够带来积极的能量和好运。这款手串通常以细致的手工制作而成，每颗水晶珠都经过精心挑选，串成手链，展现出优雅的光泽和天然的美感。福禄迭至水晶手串不仅适合佩戴，还可以作为一种具有美好祝愿的礼物，传达对他人的祝福和关怀。佩戴这款手串可以让人感受到内心的宁静与平和，同时也能成为日常穿搭的点睛之笔，增添亮点和美感。', '["https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/02e2217d-ebd8-4ee1-8241-62f73e5ce363.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/cabe2fc1-cd9d-4e1a-9cfb-e7570bec14ac.jpg"]', '限定', 1),
	(52, '2024-03-17 14:52:03', '2024-03-17 14:52:03', 23, 23, '福禄绵长系列白玉首饰', 8, 7, 15999.00, 100, 'https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/f63c99c4-db0c-4da4-8e69-50c575eeee44.jpg', '["https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/a4f85bae-1268-4620-8964-9f818018034d.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/85c9a308-ac13-4db7-b1f3-ae87d6f19da3.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/dce2872e-f713-4552-8092-2e3e36ecb0a2.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/aa511794-138a-47f0-8d62-4f12c00ae619.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/246d0908-555b-4638-b0b0-025f92740d42.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/7781da3e-fd8b-4d58-96f8-40468358ce3b.jpg"]', '福禄绵长系列白玉首饰以白玉为主要材质制成，代表着幸福、富贵和长寿的象征。这一系列的首饰设计精美，包括项链、手镯、耳环等，每一件都展现了高品质的工艺和精湛的设计。白玉的自然纹理和光泽使得每件首饰看起来独一无二，散发着迷人的光芒。福禄绵长系列白玉首饰不仅适合日常佩戴，也是搭配正装的完美选择，展现出优雅与高贵。这些首饰不仅能够提升整体气质，还能成为送礼的不错选择，传达祝福和美好的愿望。佩戴这些首饰可以让人感受到内心的宁静与平和，同时也能成为日常穿搭的点睛之笔，增添亮点和美感。', '["https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/53f05f6a-8555-4afa-a6a0-c404af23d87a.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/94785ffc-6b21-49ea-a61b-ad65291d7326.jpg"]', '限量', 1),
	(53, '2024-03-17 14:53:21', '2024-03-17 14:53:21', 23, 23, '事事如意系列首饰', 8, 7, 29999.00, 10, 'https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/b36c7166-78fd-4904-aa64-69cbf95609da.jpg', '["https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/e26b22ad-564e-4725-89de-375cd20c2388.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/164cc097-993e-46ea-9ca4-98aeaad1958e.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/680ace73-c1ad-4368-bdb6-4c90934bd1d5.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/00d7c6a2-9527-4e5e-87a4-cb216f84b556.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/06816834-96ab-4f31-916c-ef20fe2a1ee2.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/864f8ddc-4fca-486d-8ea2-efd16ebb366a.jpg"]', '事事如意系列首饰是一款具有美好寓意的饰品系列，旨在传达吉祥如意、幸福美满的祝福。这一系列的首饰设计精美，通常以精致的工艺制成，包括项链、手镯、耳环等，每一件都展现了高品质的制作和精湛的设计。饰品常常搭配一些吉祥图案或者寓意吉祥的吉祥语，如如意、福禄寿喜等。这些首饰不仅能够提升整体气质，还能成为送礼的不错选择，传达祝福和美好的愿望。佩戴这些首饰可以让人感受到内心的宁静与平和，同时也能成为日常穿搭的点睛之笔，增添亮点和美感。', '["https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/9c974843-d74a-43bc-aaa9-31b945ff1fe7.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/cf332234-d03d-4834-8693-778641f105eb.jpg"]', '限量', 1),
	(54, '2024-03-17 14:55:28', '2024-03-17 14:55:28', 23, 23, '鹤舞青松丝巾', 13, 7, 999.00, 1000, 'https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/3620e4f6-f5bc-44e4-9893-91684de73b99.jpg', '["https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/e02a8269-daa8-46ea-816f-75b56957293e.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/872254c9-273c-4744-81aa-a756f26710fa.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/f9371bd3-d127-4b0e-aa32-48b7e92e1d63.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/e15d980d-927e-4f68-9817-1546c965fd28.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/fbd6733f-0cc1-432c-b10f-d88df98acbd5.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/b6884432-8115-4e76-a60a-837566193955.jpg"]', '鹤舞青松丝巾是一款精美的丝质面料制成的围巾，通常以鹤舞和青松等优美图案或者寓意吉祥的图案进行装饰。这款丝巾通常采用优质的丝绸材料制成，具有柔软光滑的手感和光泽。其设计灵感常常来自中国传统文化中的吉祥元素，如鹤和青松，象征着长寿、吉祥和幸福。这样的丝巾在日常穿搭中既能增添亮点，又能展现出优雅的气质。它不仅可以作为配饰搭配服装，还可以作为礼物送给亲朋好友，传达对他们的祝福和关怀。鹤舞青松丝巾的设计精美，寓意美好，是一款值得收藏和佩戴的精美饰品。', '["https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/d7ece9e0-79a2-4ef3-b5f6-e71848809262.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/747d8bb1-6641-49c1-9d05-f95b9a8d721a.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/b0e8c0b3-45a2-40ea-ac07-3752e29fb2bc.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/040c2891-2638-4b44-b652-13b4bed45608.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/706441e8-8eac-4fd0-a607-ae5acc789641.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/277a223d-c5c2-409c-a609-4b3b3e6d74d9.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/b278a9a2-c5a2-463c-9c4d-aa8af964376a.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/5c2ee3c2-740a-4efc-9c67-1bdcd82a6fb0.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/2826ec88-9270-4f64-afd1-41bd11a3bf89.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/49677dec-d7a6-4bd9-ab29-948fe2c5b5c8.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj