	(55, '2024-03-17 14:57:09', '2024-03-17 14:57:09', 23, 23, '珍宝庄严丝巾', 13, 7, 798.00, 1200, 'https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/3a87a218-ba9e-41f5-a791-ddb8f674d43c.jpg', '["https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/09ba1cfd-17d1-4f37-b2c8-7e25b33f7158.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/4437a70f-1e32-436c-9441-48078608a635.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/1fb0b2fe-6706-4d1c-a855-eef4ed4c9b54.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/202f1a04-bb48-4fd4-bf21-cc2341e540a1.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/e8436800-fe73-49f3-bc74-35e96f3b227f.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/6ef51c58-dd46-4120-a44e-996d5a7f1eb0.jpg"]', '珍宝庄严丝巾是一款精美的丝质面料制成的围巾，通常以庄严肃穆的图案和富丽堂皇的设计闻名。这款丝巾通常采用优质的丝绸材料制成，具有柔软光滑的手感和细腻的光泽。其设计常常融合了中国传统文化中的庄重元素和寓意吉祥的图案，如龙凤、寿桃等，展现出华贵和典雅。这样的丝巾在日常穿搭中既能增添亮点，又能展现出高贵的气质。它不仅可以作为配饰搭配服装，还可以作为珍贵的礼物，传达对亲朋好友的祝福和关怀。珍宝庄严丝巾的设计精美，充满着文化内涵，是一款值得收藏和佩戴的精美饰品。', '["https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/f3f5cc9d-3d07-4ff2-bd5f-1e698bdc23bc.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/8e66bf0a-121c-4d24-b877-26e549556f04.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/1144f86c-f9bf-4f4c-bd47-b7811710af57.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/1b3a267d-ba11-47aa-af64-e5a5ba308e44.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/e09d1be2-75c7-43d6-b084-821492001fbf.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/4d4f042d-872b-475f-a25f-6286869d76e1.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/096b62d3-62b4-4fd9-b287-312ec4b01793.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/d0fcfd35-63e2-407d-8924-cc6e34afb8ec.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/a86eb755-2b0c-49c8-9944-be63e509595e.jpg","https://web-framework-cwj.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/fc1eb87b-499a-4813-afe2-4637bead107d.jpg"]', '真丝', 1),
